{"tid":1651943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人可唔可以應承我，人權法案過咗都好，要保持憤怒","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T16:12:02.000Z","uid":4705,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd058d01b46b5850df4d5a9caaf8bc54602407e","tid":1651943,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"雖然呢場運動係冇大台，但大家都好睇重國際戰線，一直都好依賴美國，每日一大堆白宮聯署，每日揮美國國旗<br />\n<br />\n最近為咗個人權法案通過，做咩都諗畫面好唔好睇、會唔會影響到人權法案通過，每日都諗好多。但係大家真係唔可以太依賴美國，太依賴呢個人權法案，我哋同美國都只係相互利用嘅關係，對美國嚟講我哋都只係撚鳩中共嘅其中一隻棋<br />\n<br />\n自從吹咗休息風之後，大家都真係休息得好充足，我好擔心呢兩日人權法案過咗之後，大家就以為贏咗，繼續休息等美國慢慢制裁港共同黑警。但係大家仲記唔記得我哋有五大訴求，而人權法案係爭取唔到呢五大訴求㗎？<br />\n<br />\n各位手足可唔可以應承我，無論人權法案過唔過都好，一定要保持憤怒，為死咗嘅手足討回公道，繼續爭取五大訴求呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都好，聽晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行出嚟話比美國知，我哋有幾想呢個人權法案通過啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lr1trOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLr1trOn.jpg&h=13db6b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfLRpz3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfLRpz3.jpg&h=4db248f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4d29d3ec0e8dd08fdaffb119a7034fad7ab282f","tid":1651943,"uid":14303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9177c03387fc7b12dcd4fdd3f5438d13734a234","tid":1651943,"uid":141070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"無人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3021e01b7af4d66ba93d50ec402ce4482416d422","tid":1651943,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9177c03387fc7b12dcd4fdd3f5438d13734a234","tid":1651943,"uid":141070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"無人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"睇完金宵大廈冇嘢做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd516e498612ed3a275dfb7da5d6d6c86c207148","tid":1651943,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"（VTC同學速入)讓陳同學沉冤得雪！！！還其家人一個公道！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話，幫手推同share岀去，等聽日多啲人集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求幫手推呢個先，聽日要人，但我地唔想提早俾校方知而令佢地關校，所以咁夜先岀稿，求share至fb,ws,tg各群組<br />\n另外，部分ive設施對公眾開放的"}]}